// ============================================================================

/**
 * TOTAL LETTER TYPES: 150+
 * 
 * Category Breakdown:
 * - Government Outreach: 14 types
 * - Investor Relations: 12 types
 * - Partnership Outreach: 13 types
 * - Legal Notices: 14 types
 * - Regulatory: 14 types
 * - Banking & Finance: 14 types
 * - Media & PR: 10 types
 * - Employment: 14 types
 * - Customer Relations: 14 types
 * - Supplier Relations: 14 types
 * - Acknowledgments: 13 types
 * - Diplomatic: 10 types
 * 
 * Formality Levels: Highly Formal, Formal, Semi-Formal, Professional
 * 
 * Output Formats: PDF, DOCX
 * 
 * AI Capabilities per Letter:
 * - Precedent matching (historical examples)
 * - Cultural adaptation (regional etiquette)
 * - Legal language optimization
 * - Compliance checking
 * - Stakeholder intelligence
 */

